    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis.<persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/32"> Karolus </persName>divina
                        favente clementia<rs key="#Emperor/king"> imperator </rs>augustus. Si
                        petitionibus fidelium nostrorum maxime eorum, qui nostro fideliter parent
                        imperio, aures celsitudinis nostre accomodamus, non solum imperialem in hoc
                        exercemus dignitatem, verum etiam eterne retributionis premia inde nobis
                        largiri procul dubio credimus. Quapropter cognoscat omnium fidelium
                        nostrorum presentium videlicet et futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/33"
                            >Liutuuardum </persName>venerabilem <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs> et
                        dilectum <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicanzellarium</rs> nostram postulasse
                        serenitatem, ut sanctissimo <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/81"
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Curtes #Plebs #Districtio #Baptismal_churches #Bishops"
                            >patri Eusebio</orgName> defensori christiane fidei aliqua de iure regni
                        nostri concederemus et aliqua que subtracta sunt redderemus. Statimque nos
                        postulationes illius saluberrimas agnoscentes decrevimus ita fieri.
                        Concessimus itaque prefato sancto Eusebio cortem nostram magnam que dicitur
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Fiscal_property #Object #Tolls #Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#estates/60"><placeName
                                ref="#places/48"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object">Regio
                        </placeName></geogName>antiquo nuncupatur vulgo cum tota<rs key="#Forests">
                            silva </rs>eiusdem et <placeName ref="#places/49"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object">fulgitio</placeName> et cum omnibus
                        cortibus et villis, cum <placeName key="#Fiscal_property #Object"
                            ref="#places/103">valle Cliui</placeName> et
                        omnibus eorum pertinentiis simul cum corte de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/99"
                            ><placeName>Roueredo</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus suis
                        adiacentiis, dedimus etiam <rs key="#Curtes">cortem </rs>nostram magnam que
                        dicitur <geogName key="#Curtes #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/62"><placeName
                                ref="#places/50" key="#Curtes">Bugella
                            </placeName></geogName>cum omnibus cortibus et villis alpibus et omnibus
                        suis pertinentiis, contulimus et reddidimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/63"><placeName
                                ref="#places/51"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                                >Sestinium</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus alpibus et
                        pertinentiis suis, ut muris sanctis in censuali calce perpetuo deserviret,
                        donavimus et restituimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/88">Romanianum</geogName> cum
                        omnibus suis vallibus alpibus et suis pertinentiis, et confirmavimus totam
                            <rs key="#Forests">silvam </rs><placeName key="#Forests"
                            ref="#places/96">Rouasindam
                        </placeName>pertinentem ad <rs key="#Plebs #Baptismal_churches">plebem
                            </rs><orgName key="#Plebs #Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/83">sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName> ipsius Vercellensis ecclesie, reddidimus et
                            confirmavimus<rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"> pontem </rs><placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Bridges/pontoons"
                            ref="#places/104">Notingum</placeName>,
                            quem<persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/109">
                            Notingus</persName> episcopus eiusdem <placeName
                            ref="#places/106" key="#Bishops"
                            >Vercellensis</placeName> ecclesie mirabiliter super eum equitando per
                        legem recepit, dedimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/89"><placeName
                                ref="#places/107" key="#Curtes"
                                >Trecade</placeName>
                        </geogName>cum omnibus suis pertinentiis, dedimus <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/96">cortem iuris nostri <placeName
                                key="#Curtes" ref="#places/99"
                                >Firminianam</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis,
                        obtulimus et restituimus cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/41"><placeName
                                ref="#places/3" key="#Curtes">Carixianam
                            </placeName></geogName>cum <placeName
                            ref="#places/100" key="#Fiscal_property #Object"
                            >Langusco</placeName> sibi adiacente et cum omnibus suis pertinentiis,
                        largiti sumus et reddidimus cortes de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/97"><placeName
                                ref="#places/101"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property">Pasiliano</placeName></geogName> et
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Districtio #Tolls #Teloneum"
                            ref="#estates/98"><placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/105"
                            >Occimiano</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis. Hec
                        omnia sancta Vercellensis ecclesia proprio iure in eternum habeat cum
                        omnibus publicis <rs key="#Districtio">districtis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Tolls #Teloneum"> teloneum </rs><rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">piscationibus</rs>
                        venationibus portibus molendinis montibus et vallibus alpibus edificiis
                        mancipiis utriusque sexus agris vineis capellis pratis pascuis silvis aquis
                        aquarumque decursibus cultis et incultis et de nostro iure et dominio in ius
                        et dominium prelibate ecclesie tradimus atque transfundimus. Si quis autem
                        hanc nostram traditionem infringere temptaverit, eiusdem piissimi Eusebii
                        iram incurrat, insuper rectoribus ecclesie persolvendum centum libras auri
                        purissimi culpabilis habeatur. Et ut hec traditio pleniorem in dei nomine
                        obtineat firmitatem, hoc nostre auctoritatis preceptum fieri mandavimus
                        propriaque manu confirmantes anulo nostro iussimus sigillari. Signum (M.)
                        domni Karoli serenissimi imperatoris augusti. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
